Perfect! Now I have all the information. Let me compile a comprehensive report for you:

## Complete `.profile-postcards-parent-container` Analysis

I've found everything related to this container. Here's a comprehensive breakdown:

---

### 1. CSS Rules for `.profile-postcards-parent-container`

**File:** `C:\Users\johnm\iskrib_v3\client\src\components\HomePage\postCards\ProfilePostCards\profilepostcards.css`

```css
.profile-postcards-parent-container {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    align-items: center;
    width: 90%;
    padding: 1.25rem;
